    "entry": "選球",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "せんきゅう",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞",
        "動詞-サ変",
        "動詞-自動詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "waiting for a good hit at a pitch",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "ベテラン打者は、相手投手の甘い球を待つ選球眼で、フォアボールを選んだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「今のバッター、全然振らないね。」「うん、選球がしっかりしてるみたい。カウントを悪くしないのが上手い。」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "コーチは若手選手に「選球眼を磨け。無駄なアウトは減らせるぞ」とアドバイスした。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
